{"tid":2196553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球321團體促聯國查中共侵人權","createTime":"2020-09-10T04:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T05:08:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5795a6bf2ab5ef1d144bf6dfadb16347be566b3","tid":2196553,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/I3U5DJ5JZJELPPJUQNAF35DJYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FI3U5DJ5JZJELPPJUQNAF35DJYI%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=665d4104\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FI3U5DJ5JZJELPPJUQNAF35DJYI%2F&h=7c69fafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/I3U5DJ5JZJELPPJUQNAF35DJYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n全球321團體促聯國查中共侵人權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x9ULgOVFVpfDmycGz8X9QHQPBuM=/6720x4016/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KQZZZH6PMNBHFNXZY65JAOE4JY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx9ULgOVFVpfDmycGz8X9QHQPBuM%3D%2F6720x4016%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKQZZZH6PMNBHFNXZY65JAOE4JY.jpg&h=4c3a3d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■公開信促聯合國成立獨立機制，以解決中國侵犯人權的行為。<br />\n<br />\n全球圍中！海外港人組織「香港民主委員會」等全球321個公民社會團體組成的聯盟，昨日以公開信批評中國不斷打壓內地人權，也扭曲聯合國人權理事會職權，阻撓部份非政府組織（NGO）諮詢地位，促請聯合國緊急成立一個獨立的國際機制，以解決中國侵犯人權的行為。<br />\n<br />\n公開信寫道，50名聯合國人權專員今年6月26日史無前例地呼籲「為維護中國的基本自由採取果斷措施」。他們特別指出香港、西藏和新疆的人權被大規模地侵犯，疫情期間禁止訊息流通，對內地人權維護者、記者、律師和批評政府人士的迫害。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n160組織促撤京冬奧主辦權<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，超過160個人權團體與組織向國際奧委會發信，敦促糾正讓北京舉辦2022冬奧會的「錯誤決定」。信中批評中國在新疆西藏大搞「奧威爾式」監視，破壞香港一國兩制、消除蒙古文化、武嚇台灣，「如果在中國控制下的所有地區不斷惡化的人權危機被忽略，奧林匹克精神和奧林匹克聲譽將受到進一步損害」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n人權監察組織網站/美聯社"},{"pid":"1c70b603286a019bfc5ded56b717d5b3b2f54143","tid":2196553,"uid":133033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"就讓暴風雨"},{"pid":"28dc58c0ecce03708d52923916f291b604f23a3b","tid":2196553,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"就暴猛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}